{"id": "1416853158562500649", "channel_id": "1416853158562500649", "author_id": "147364225411579904", "author_name": "strandiel", "content": "Hi, I'm trying to translate the WoD banners into German; the text is different between banners and I assume it should be consistent. My instinct would be to go with Corpo's description, since it's identical to Doresain's description, and that guy had everything translated by a human. Would it be okay to match every description to that one, even if the CN/EN text doesn't match fully?\n\nSo I'd use both of these as templates:\n[<SummonOrange:Oath of the Hollowed>] Limited Wheel of Destiny Event Awakening is available!\\nDuring the event, the SSR WoD <SummonOrange:Kiss of Repose> enjoys boosted drop rate.\\nExcept for special rules (e.g., rate boosts, guarantees), all drops use base probabilities. See Rules for details.\\nDaily Discount: 60 Silver Prime per Awakening (+60 Silver bonus).\\n\\n<Title:[Balance Adjustment]>\\nBecause of Morimens' unique gameplay, Awakeners or Wheels of Destiny may be buffed or nerfed via balance adjustments to ensure fun and fairness.\\nIf nerfed, a Limited-Time Reset event allows resource refunds.\\nPlease acknowledge this before investing resources.\\n\\n\n\n<Title:[SSR Items]>\\nIn the [<SummonOrange:Oath of the Hollowed>] Limited WoD Event Awakening, the base probability for SSR items is 3.03%, with overall probability (including guarantees) of 5.00%. All SSR items are Wheels of Destiny, with a guaranteed SSR WoD after maximum 30 Awakenings.\\nWhen obtaining an SSR WoD through Awakening, there is a 50.00% chance it will be the current Rate-Up SSR <SummonOrange:Kiss of Repose>.\\nIf the last SSR WoD obtained was not the Rate-Up SSR WoD, the next SSR WoD will be guaranteed to be the Rate-Up SSR WoD.\\n\\n<Title:[SR Items]>\\nIn the [<SummonOrange:Oath of the Hollowed>] WoD Event Awakening, the base probability for SR items is 15.85%, with overall probability (including guarantees) of 25.00%. All SR items obtained will be Wheels of Destiny.\\nGuaranteed SR or higher item every 5 Awakenings, with: \\n96.97% chance for SR item\\n3.03% chance to upgrade to SSR item.\\n\\n<Title:[Special Notes]>\\nAdditional rewards per Awakening: \\nSSR Wheel of Destiny: 50 Radix Sediments\\nSR Wheel of Destiny: 5 Radix Sediments\\nR Wheel of Destiny: 1 Radix Sediment\\nThis Awakening belongs to the [WoD Event Awakening]: \\nPity count carries over between all [WoD Event Awakening], and maintains separate counter from other Awakening types.\\n\\n", "timestamp": "2025-09-14T18:28:36.860000+00:00", "thread_id": "1416853158562500649", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-15T12:50:49.033000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1416853158944051270", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 221218, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1416853158562500649/1416853158944051270/image.png?ex=6a323e94&is=6a30ed14&hm=b8efb2418091b3e5d47ff274ab371411b3b56a6eb68b8c25077c149d2a8c77b8&"}, {"id": "1416853159468601635", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 299542, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1416853158562500649/1416853159468601635/image.png?ex=6a323e95&is=6a30ed15&hm=66eb06b7ed06a396b946acf6592b91c8249011073c486583511078655b3f83d8&"}, {"id": "1416853159879639213", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 13454, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1416853158562500649/1416853159879639213/image.png?ex=6a323e95&is=6a30ed15&hm=596a6654fd0d04a42dcd5ba06da51e0082640f9ed32008d740ea71d8c7a17868&"}]}
